<i>see me run with the girls</i> ♪

17:37.389 --> 17:39.099
♪<i> I'm on top, I'm on top</i> ♪

17:39.183 --> 17:40.642
♪<i> I'm on top of the world</i> ♪

17:40.726 --> 17:42.102
♪<i> Need a break, then I'll take</i> ♪

17:42.186 --> 17:44.188
♪<i> To the top of the world</i> ♪

17:44.271 --> 17:46.106
♪<i> On my knees, all my life</i> ♪

17:46.190 --> 17:49.359
♪<i> I've been sold a chase...</i> ♪

