<i>(whispering voices continue)</i>

17:53.030 --> 17:55.365
<i>GIRL:</i>
<i>I just want to be like her.</i>

17:58.368 --> 18:00.829
Hey, it's Debbie, right?

18:00.913 --> 18:03.165
Hi. We're sitting here.

18:04.208 --> 18:06.335
Why don't you take your...

18:06.418 --> 18:07.961
tuna fish sandwich

18:08.045 --> 18:11.173
and your french fries
somewhere else?

18:12.424 --> 18:15.803
Let's go, let's go, let's go!

18:15.886 --> 18:17.346
Or do you want me
to tell everyone

18:17.429 --> 18:21.975
how you saw your stepdad
jerking it to QVC?

18:22.059 --> 18:24.019
(laughs)

18:24.102 --> 18:26.438
(quietly):
And watched him finish.

18:33.111 --> 18:35.072
-(gasps)
-(laughter)

18:59.012 --> 19:00.764
<i>MADISON:</i>
<i>Irene, did you...</i>

19:00.848 --> 19:02.933
<i>do your makeup different?</i>

